author: markt
msg: Correct the documentation for deployOnStartup to make clear that if a WAR file is updated while Tomcat is stopped and unpackWARs is true, Tomcat will not detect the changed WAR file when it starts and will not replace the unpacked WAR file with the contents of the updated WAR.
